    {
      "name": "DESTOPT",
      "description": "Destination options",
      "help": "Destination options (DESTOPT)\n\nSpecifies the destination-dependent options. When CNNTYPE(*IP) is specified, the destination-dependent options are added to the control file which is sent to the remote LPD server. When CNNTYPE(*SNA) is specified, this field is used to determine how spooled files are handled once they are sent to the remote system.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *SAME, *NONE, *USRDFNTXT, *NOWAIT",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*SAME",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 128
