    {
      "name": "USRDFNOPT",
      "description": "User defined option",
      "help": "User-defined options (USRDFNOPT)\n\nSpecifies, for spooled output only, one or more user-defined options to be used by user applications or user-specified programs that process spooled files. A maximum of four user-defined options can be specified.\n\nSingle values\n\nOther values (up to 4 repetitions)\n\n指定できる特殊値: *SAME, *NONE",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*SAME",
      "attributes": {
