    {
      "name": "USRDFNOBJ",
      "description": "User defined object",
      "help": "User-defined object (USRDFNOBJ)\n\nSpecifies, for spooled output only, the user-defined object to be used by user applications or user-specified programs that process spooled files.\n\nSingle values\n\nElement 1: Object\n\nQualifier 1: Object\n\nQualifier 2: Library\n\nElement 2: Object type",
